<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink346">
<l>avarō vārār tāṉvan taṉṟē</l>
<l>yañciṉaip pātiri yalarnteṉac</l>
<l>ceṅka ṇiruṅkuyi laṟaiyum poḻutē</l>
      </lg>
     <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Won’t he himself come? The season has arrived,</l>
<l>when trumpet flower tree with beautiful branches bloom,</l>
<l>and black cuckoos with red eyes sing.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
